flowchart LR
classDef user fill:#e1f5ff,stroke:#01579b
classDef prompt fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32
classDef context fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00
classDef rag fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#6a1b9a
classDef model fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c62828
A[用户原始输入]:::user --> B[Prompt 工程化<br/>明确任务要求]:::prompt
B --> C[Context 组装<br/>当前可见信息总和]:::context
C --> D{信息是否足够?}
D -->|否| E[RAG 检索<br/>外部知识补录]:::rag
E --> C
D -->|是| F[LLM 生成输出]:::model
